# Drizzle

<center>![Drizzle](../Drizzle-logo.png)</center>

[Drizzle](http://www.drizzle.org/) is a community-driven open source project
that is forked from the popular MySQL database. The Drizzle team has removed
non-essential code, re-factored the remaining code into a plugin-based
architecture and modernized the code base moving to C++.

